channel.title: Bots
channel.description: So, I recently found an old version of ausbot and I'm playing around with it, seeing if its any use. Any idea how to find a servers ip/port?

item.title: Bots
item.dc:creator: @NoLives NoLives
item.description:
@NoLives wrote:

[quote="-Nothing, post:4, topic:430036"][quote author=NoLives link=topic=532717.msg3893843#msg3893843 date=1327148362]

So, I recently found an old version of ausbot and I’m playing around with it, seeing if its any use.
Any idea how to find a servers ip/port?

It’s pretty easy to make it work for any server, server ip and port is located at GameWindowMiddleMan class.
[/quote]Alright, found the ip/port, now, how to find the client version?
oh also, tell me ur actualy msn, since ur not on the one you used for rscf.

Well I thought you blocked me since you weren’t on anymore o.O, I haven’t been on MSN for days though.[/quote]Oh, sorry, I forgot about my 2nd one.
I’ll go on, be there
